These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, cabbage, carrot, lettuce
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, scientific, musical, thriller
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, mexican, pakistani, russian
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hamster, horse, rat
 1. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 2. the person eating banana is in an even position##4
 3. the brazilian is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
 4. the pakistani is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 5. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
 7. the mexican is the person eating carrot##1
 8. the owner of the horse is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the rat and the person watching thriller movies##2
10. the person eating banana is the owner of the rat##1
11. the person watching musical movies is the person eating lettuce##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | carrot  | banana    | lettuce    | cabbage   |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific     | satire   | musical       | thriller    |
| Nationality   | mexican | brazilian | russian    | pakistani |
| Pet           | hamster | rat       | chinchilla | horse     |

