 1. the bluemaster-smoker is in an odd position##4
 2. the chaman-smoker is between the bluemaster-smoker and the swisher-smoker##2
 3. the american is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 4. the person watching sports movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the spanish is on the right of the nigerian##1
 6. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
 7. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the australian##1
 9. the chaman-smoker is between the american and the person watching fantasy movies##2
10. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
11. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an even position##4
12. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3

.:: Answer ::.
