House: tower, gothic-revival, art-deco, townhouse
 1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
 2. the person eating grapes is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the tower house##3
 4. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 5. the art-deco house is in an odd position##4
 6. the person drinking juice is the tower house##1
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the tower house##1
 8. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 9. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the person eating grapes is on the right of the tower house##1
11. the person eating cucumber is on the far left##1
12. the person drinking juice is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2    |     3     |       4       |
