The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, hip-hop, house, punk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, golf, surfing, skiing
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, roller, subway, train
 1. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
 2. the person who's sport is surfing is the person driving the train##1
 3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
 4. the person who's sport is surfing is the fan of house##1
 5. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 6. the person watching spy movies is in an odd position##4
 7. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
 8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
 9. the fan of punk is in an even position##4
10. the fan of gospel is between the person watching spy movies and the person who's sport is surfing##2
11. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
12. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | horror  | spy      | family   |
| Music-Genre   | house  | gospel  | hip-hop  | punk     |
