.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, juice, milk
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, dannemann, havana, tiparillo
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, satire, sports, western
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, sailing, volleyball, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the havana-smoker is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 7. the dannemann-smoker is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the siglo-smoker##3
10. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
11. the person watching western movies is in an odd position##4
12. the siglo-smoker is the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | juice       | hot-chocolate | 7up        | milk        |
| Cigar         | tiparillo | havana       | siglo | dannemann |
| Movie-Genre   | western     | satire        | mystery    | sports      |
| Sport         | sailing     | volleyball    | water-polo | badminton   |

