.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, house, pop, techno
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, azalea, dahlia, amaryllis
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, parkour, rugby, water-polo
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, helicopter, skateboard
 1. the fan of techno is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 2. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person who growspoppy and the person who growsamaryllis##2
 3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
 4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
 5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 6. the fan of house is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
 8. the person who growsamaryllis is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
10. the person who growspoppy is in an even position##4
11. the person who growspoppy is on the far right##1
12. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | house      | ambient | techno     | pop        |
| Flower   | dahlia | amaryllis  | azalea     | poppy |
| Sport         | parkour    | cycling | rugby      | water-polo |
| Transport     | skateboard | car     | helicopter | bike       |

 